platforms         darwin
license           LGPL-2.1+
homepage          http://ktoblzcheck.sourceforge.net/
master_sites      sourceforge
checksums         md5     80719a2920a40c6a01fa2a70ecc23e48 \
                  sha1    a552012bb219ac24dcdbac977cf94c951bfe31bc \
